The task is to create an app that replaces a facial expression with an emodji

Project description:
    The task is to create an app that finds all faces on a video and replaces them with an emodji, wich corresponds to persons facial expression
    
Restrictions:
    * There are only 6 emotions so far: sadness, happiness, fear, anger, disgust, surprise
    * Classifier will only work on a full face turned to the camera
    * Nice lighting wil be a great plus too 

To run the project simply launch demo.py 
New model could be trained using training/classifier_features.py


Databases used: 
    --- The Extended Cohn-Kanade Dataset (CK+) and can be found at http://www.consortium.ri.cmu.edu/ckagree/. 
    --- The Japanese Female Facial Expression (JAFFE). JAFFE can be found here: http://www.kasrl.org/jaffe.html
    --- http://app.visgraf.impa.br/database/faces/ - faces database